DE QUOI S OCCUPE VAULT ->
Backend API  →  PostgreSQL   (DB_PASSWORD, credentials)
Backend API  →  JWT / Auth   (JWT_SECRET, API_KEYS)
Prometheus   →  scrape       (pas de secret Vault nécessaire)
Grafana      →  dashboard    (GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD si besoin)
NGINX        →  reverse proxy (certs TLS potentiellement)


